{"tid":409434,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS4 FIFA18 球員預先招募","createTime":"2017-09-22T05:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T08:42:51.000Z","uid":70926,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"296cbee77f8b893e44a389920c069d7476ad9120","tid":409434,"uid":70926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:00:03.000Z","msg":"已有固定班底（4-5人）<br />\n陣型：視乎上線人數而定<br />\n開波時間：<br />\n8:00-1:00 （一至五） <br />\n不定（六/日）<br />\n<br />\n主要踢法：控傳，小組，one touch，one two，tiki taka，小量燒味<br />\n<br />\n現招： <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">前場</span>：1名<br />\nhold到波，多one touch，知幾時走直線，幾時接應<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">中場</span>：1-2名<br />\n防中（球隊支柱）<br />\n翼（可能會間中客串LW/RW，淨係識落底斬中就不了)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">後場</span>：2-3名<br />\n人數不足時，可轉踢防中<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Keeper</span>：1名<br />\n有經驗，勁過電腦就得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">非常</span>注重團隊合作，所以謝絕球霸call霸<br />\n<br />\n最好開咪一齊踢，有wtsapp group，平時人少可能會轉玩其他Game（最近玩緊2k18），歡迎多修人士<br />\n<br />\n有意加我tg：lung94628"},{"pid":"7541ec19c25621931a233849f877d04417d3d681","tid":409434,"uid":103749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:04:52.000Z","msg":"Tg Pmed"},{"pid":"d31fd8d822ccea60720f26289bee9022922da465","tid":409434,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:36:22.000Z","msg":"lm定先"},{"pid":"e55b840cc07e66c03c71589562ea8532f0d803b5","tid":409434,"uid":70926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:16:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74a93e1f59e8c33172883aae28bb9e5641e06c8d","tid":409434,"uid":38934,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:18:03.000Z","msg":"8-1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返一份工仲唔夠咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af96212c5dcc8317e45b5ae74aac93442c7af226","tid":409434,"uid":70926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"